quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Praise the limitless glory of your Lord's name, the Most High"
  87,2,Who created and proportioned
  87,3,"Who destined and [then] guided"
  87,4,He who brought out the green pasture
  87,5,and then made it black stubble
  87,6,"We will make you recite, and you will not forget"
  87,7,except what God wills. He knows what is open to one's perception and what is hidden
  87,8,And We will ease you toward the easy way
  87,9,"So, remind, if reminding helps"
  87,10,He who fears God will remember
  87,11,But the most wicked will ignore it
  87,12,He will kindle the greatest fire
  87,13,"where he will remain, neither dying nor living"
  87,14,Successful is he who purifies himself
  87,15,and remembers to call on his Lord and pray
  87,16,But you prefer this worldly life
  87,17,whereas the Hereafter is better and more enduring
  87,18,All this is can be found in the earlier Scriptures
  87,19,the Scriptures of Abraham and Moses